### User Register

POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"test",
    "lastName":"user",
    "email":"test@gmail.com",
    "password":"test@123",
    "profileImageUrl":"images/test.jpg"
}


