### block user
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/block
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "admin" : "698ac07a7cfdb430ff1971c1",
    "user" : "69896c47f4a7c8024395545e"
}



### Unblock user
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/unblock
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "admin" : "698ac07a7cfdb430ff1971c1",
    "user" : "69896c47f4a7c8024395545e"
}


